271
00:12:10,896 --> 00:12:12,965
That's why yukgaejang,

272
00:12:13,032 --> 00:12:15,134
a spicy beef stew, was created.

273
00:12:15,201 --> 00:12:18,838
The origin of the yukgaejang we eat today
was called the Daegu stew,

274
00:12:18,904 --> 00:12:22,241
which tells us that yukgaejang
originated in Daegu.

275
00:12:24,176 --> 00:12:26,979
Yukgaejang follows
Daegu's traditional style.

276
00:12:27,046 --> 00:12:29,949
We simmer beef leg bones for 24 hours

277
00:12:30,015 --> 00:12:32,651
and 365 days a year.

278
00:12:33,085 --> 00:12:34,353
After boiling them,

279
00:12:34,420 --> 00:12:37,423
